# Pomodoro Timer

A simple Python-based Pomodoro Timer to help manage work and break intervals. Customize work duration, short break duration, and long break duration.

## Features
- Countdown timer for work sessions and breaks
- Customizable session length
- Default values for quick use

## Usage
1. Clone the repository.
2. Run `PomodoroTimer.py` in your preferred Python environment.
3. Follow the prompts to set your work and break times.

## Future Enhancements
- Sound alerts at the end of each session
- Pause and resume functionality
- Graphical user interface (GUI)
